  "text": "Volatility and loading tests were evaluated via LC analysis, using an Agilent Technologies 1120 Compact LC, equipped with a Zorbax Eclipse Plus C18 column (Agilent Technologies, UK). Samples were analysed using isocratic ratio 80 : 20 (acetonitrile: H 2 O), UV detector (l ¼ 270 nm), flow of 1 ml min [CITATION_1] and an injection volume of 10 ml (3 ml for loading tests) over 4 min. Calibration curves for both compounds were constructed using these LC parameters to determine the loading capacity of the MSNPs.",
